Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Las{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}- Gemas de{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}- Cristal{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Te ayudan si estás mal{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Y no hay complicación{\c}{\i0}
